-- Egypt forecasts economic growth above 3 pct in 2014/15 fiscal year
-- By Asma Alsharif
-- Mon Jun 30, 2014 07:27AM EDT
-- None



CAIRO, June 30 (Reuters) - Egypt's economy is expected to grow by more than 3 percent during the 2014/15 fiscal year, Finance Minister Hany Kadry Dimian said on Monday, in line with previous forecasts.

